data.description: 3bdrms, 2 baths brick home situated on a culdesac with an oversized yard and 2 tier deck perfect for grilling and entertaining! Seller offering a New Stove and Dishwasher with acceptable offer!! The community also features a pond with a large deck perfect for relaxing, fishing, and kayaking.  This open layout features the great room dining room and kitchen all open to each other. Come make this one yours before it’s gone!
